OL,3,CSon stabbed mum 35 times during
OL,4,Cpsychotic episode, jury finds
OL,6,FA man inflicted the injuries which led
OL,7,Fto the death of his mother at their
OL,8,Ffamily home, a jury has found.
OL,10,FShaun Emmerson, 51, was not present at
OL,11,FLincoln Crown Court on Thursday, as a
OL,12,Fjury in a fact-finding hearing decided
OL,13,Fhe was responsible for the attack on
OL,14,Fhis mother Christine Emmerson, 71, on
OL,15,F3 August last year.
