OL,4,Cpsychotic episode, jury finds
OL,6,FMrs Emmerson was stabbed 26 times in
OL,7,Fthe neck and head, and nine times in
OL,8,Fher torso, in the living room of the
OL,9,Fhome she shared with her son and
OL,10,Fhusband, David, in Kirk Close, West
OL,11,FAshby, Lincolnshire.
OL,13,FEmmerson, who has paranoid
OL,14,Fschizophrenia and was experiencing a
OL,15,Fpsychotic episode when he killed his
OL,16,Fmother, was ruled unfit to enter a
OL,17,Fplea or take part in the trial of the
OL,18,Ffacts.
