OL,6,FThe hearing did not require jurors to
OL,7,Freturn verdicts of guilty or not
OL,8,Fguilty on charges of murder, instead
OL,9,Fbeing asked to decide whether Emmerson
OL,10,F"did the acts alleged against him".
OL,12,FAfter hearing evidence over three
OL,13,Fdays, the jury took four hours to
OL,14,Freach its unanimous decision.
OL,16,FThe court heard Emmerson climbed on to
OL,17,Fthe roof of the conservatory to call
OL,18,F999 to report that he had carried out
OL,19,Fa "violent attack" following the
OL,20,Fincident.
