OL,6,FDuring the call, Emmerson told the
OL,7,Foperator to send armed officers to
OL,8,F"put me out of my misery" and claimed
OL,9,Fthe "Department of Justice have been
OL,10,Ftorturing me for the last 20 years".
OL,12,FHe also thought he could hear his
OL,13,Fneighbours "through the walls", saying
OL,14,Fthey wanted to kill him in a "painful"
OL,15,Fway, that everyone was "evil" and that
OL,16,Fhe was afraid that someone would
OL,17,F"attack" him in his sleep.
