OL,6,FThe jury were told Emmerson's
OL,7,Fbehaviour in the weeks before he
OL,8,Fkilled his mother was a cause for
OL,9,Fconcern for his parents, who were
OL,10,Fworried he was becoming increasingly
OL,11,Fwithdrawn, spending most of his time
OL,12,Fin his bedroom or watching the news.
OL,14,FEmmerson had previously admitted to
OL,15,Fhis father, who was at work at the
OL,16,Ftime of the attack, that he may have
OL,17,Fmissed some of his prescribed
OL,18,Fmedication, which he had been taking
OL,19,Ffor about 20 years.
