OL,4,Cpsychotic episode, jury finds
OL,6,FThe night before Mrs Emmerson was
OL,7,Fkilled, Shaun Emmerson had gone down
OL,8,Fto "say goodbye" to his mother, as he
OL,9,Ffeared someone would be coming to kill
OL,10,Fhim that night, but his parents
OL,11,Freassured him he was safe.
OL,13,FA 23.5cm-long pink kitchen knife was
OL,14,Frecovered from a bedroom in the house
OL,15,Fcovered in such a large volume of Mrs
OL,16,FEmmerson's blood that the weapon could
OL,17,Fnot be DNA tested for who had held it,
OL,18,Fjurors were told.
