OL,3,CSon stabbed mum 35 times during
OL,4,Cpsychotic episode, jury finds
OL,6,FEmmerson is now facing an indefinite
OL,7,Fhospital order after the jury's
OL,8,Fruling, with sentencing due on 16 July.
OL,10,FJudge Simon Hirst said: "The only real
OL,11,Foption is a hospital order which will
OL,12,Fhave the impact of detaining him in a
OL,13,Fmental hospital until such time he is
OL,14,Fwell enough to be released, if that is
OL,15,Fever to happen."
OL,17,FAddressing the jury, Judge Hirst said:
OL,18,F"What you have heard has been deeply
OL,19,Fdistressing. You have heard about a
OL,20,Fmuch-loved grandmother, mother and
OL,21,Fwife losing her life.
